money betting the economy would burn
down."

73
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:39,510
"Did you tell anyone? Did you try and do
anything about it?" You know what I mean?

74
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:45,670
Like, listen, I made my money, you know,
I'm not an angel. But at the same time, I
care about this country and the people of
this country and the world,

75
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:52,150
and what happens to the economy. And if I
made money betting that the economy is
going to break, I feel I at least have an
obligation to try and tell people,

76
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:57,110
"Listen, this economy is gonna break.
It's breaking. I understand how. I
understand how to fix it."

77
00:06:57,120 --> 00:07:00,310
If nobody listens, then maybe I'll go
back. But I've gotta try.
